# Local-only environment overrides for `vercel dev`.
# Copy this file to .env.local (gitignored) and fill in values when needed.
#
# Nothing here is required today — the static frontend uses the publishable
# Supabase key baked into assets/js/supabase-client.js. This file becomes
# relevant once we add server-side code (Vercel Functions, scripts, etc.)
# that needs secrets such as the Supabase service_role key.

# SUPABASE_URL=https://uxgszfjjrutpfwdlahbc.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=put-the-server-only-key-here
